## Quick Start

### 1. Validate Libraries

```bash
cd teebu-shared-libs
pip install -r requirements.txt --break-system-packages
python run_all_tests.py

# Expected:
# ✓ 74 tests passed
```

### 2. Configure Business

```bash
cd saas-boilerplate
cp business/config/business_config.json.example business/config/business_config.json
# Edit with your business details
```

### 3. Start Backend

```bash
cd saas-boilerplate/backend
pip install -r requirements.txt --break-system-packages
uvicorn main:app --reload

# Logs show:
# ✓ Database initialized
# ✓ Loaded 0 business route(s)
# API ready at http://localhost:8000
```

### 4. Start Frontend

```bash
cd saas-boilerplate/frontend
npm install
npm start

# Opens http://localhost:3000
```

### 5. Add Business Logic

```bash
# Backend: drop file here
business/backend/routes/your_feature.py

# Frontend: drop file here
business/frontend/pages/YourPage.jsx

# Auto-loads on startup - zero integration
```

