# SaaS Boilerplate

**Config-driven SaaS starter for rapid deployment of multiple businesses.**

Change one JSON file → complete branded SaaS app.

---

## What You Get

**Backend (FastAPI):**
- Auth0 login/signup integration
- Stripe subscriptions + webhooks
- MailerLite email capture
- Google Analytics tracking
- RESTful API with all endpoints
- Config-driven business settings

**Frontend (React + Tailwind):**
- Home page with hero, features, testimonials
- Pricing page (loads from config)
- Login/Signup (Auth0)
- Dashboard (protected routes)
- Account settings (subscription management)
- Contact form
- Terms/Privacy pages (loads from config)
- Fully responsive

**One Config File Changes Everything:**
- Business name, tagline, colors
- All page content
- Pricing plans
- Features, testimonials
- Legal text
- Footer links

