## Backend API Endpoints

**Configuration:**
- `GET /api/config` - Get full client-safe config
- `GET /api/config/{page}` - Get specific page config

**Auth:**
- `POST /api/auth/signup` - Create user (Auth0 + MailerLite + Analytics)
- `POST /api/auth/send-verification` - Send verification email
- `POST /api/auth/password-reset` - Trigger password reset

**Subscriptions:**
- `POST /api/subscribe` - Create checkout session
- `POST /api/cancel-subscription` - Cancel subscription
- `POST /api/webhooks/stripe` - Handle Stripe webhooks

**Analytics:**
- `POST /api/analytics/track` - Track custom event
- `POST /api/analytics/page-view` - Track page view

**Contact:**
- `POST /api/contact` - Submit contact form

**User Management:**
- `GET /api/user/{user_id}` - Get user details
- `PUT /api/user/{user_id}` - Update user
- `DELETE /api/user/{user_id}` - Delete account

**Docs:**
- `GET /docs` - Interactive API documentation (Swagger)

